        "timestamp": "2018-09-20 18:27:09.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n(3 comments)\n\nPlease see my embedded comment - you should use the version of javax.ws.rs-api that comes preinstalled with ODL (2.0.1).  I think if you remove <version> tag, that should probably be set already in distributionManagement in the ODL parent that we inherit from",
        "patchset_number": 3
